When it comes to starting affiliate marketing website, there can be a lot of questions. For example, with the Amazon Associates affiliate program you will most likely need a website. Getting accepted is not that difficult as long as you make your site the correct way. You might think the design matters a lot, but the most important thing actually is the content. If you are looking to start an affiliate niche site, focus on creating quality content first, then trying to monetize it with an affiliate program like Amazon Associates.

